description: Beneath an uneven wooden ceiling, a tattered merchant permit hangs on one of the plain wooden walls.  A plain wooden table sits in one corner while a worn rug rests on the wooden floor.

The broad sweep of the blonde oak floor is interrupted by a worn rug.  Halfway to the oak beam ceiling, a tattered merchant permit hangs on one of the smooth white plaster walls.  A plain wooden table is pushed to the back of the shop.

Smooth white plaster walls rise from a golden blonde oak floor.  Just above a worn rug hangs a woven floral tapestry, and an oak beam ceiling completes the picture.  A floral-etched ceramic case and a plain wooden table stand side by side in the middle of the room.
Beneath an oak beam ceiling, a tattered merchant permit hangs on one of the smooth white plaster walls.  A plain wooden table sits in one corner while a worn rug rests on the blonde oak floor.

Enclosed by smooth white plaster walls, the shop features a glass-fronted bookcase in the center of its blonde oak floor.  A tattered merchant permit hangs under the oak beam ceiling.  Right near the front is a spacious grey slate counter and a heavy lead glass display case.

Beneath an oak beam ceiling, a tattered merchant permit hangs on one of the smooth white plaster walls.  A heavy white granite counter and a tall oak and ivory cabinet sit in opposite corners while a stuffed grizzly bear rests on a golden blonde oak floor.

A noble elf maiden portrait hangs on one of the smooth white plaster walls, and an oak beam ceiling rises overhead.  A glass-fronted bookcase sits in one corner of a golden blonde oak floor.  There is a heavy lead glass display case on one side of the shop and a spacious grey slate counter on the other.
